PUBLICAR AVALONIA AUTOMATICO


CRIAR A PASTA NO SERVIDOR NGYNX:
sudo mkdir -p /var/www/updates/erpmateus
sudo chown -R www-data:www-data /var/www/updates

-> anexar o trecho no arquivo
location /updates/ {
    alias /var/www/updates/;
    autoindex off;

    # ajuda com JSON e downloads
    types { application/json json; }

    add_header Cache-Control "no-cache" always;
}

rodar comando:
sudo nginx -t
sudo systemctl reload nginx

PUBLICAR: 
dotnet publish -c Release -r linux-x64 --self-contained true -o publish

INTALAR O VPK NO TERMINAL
dotnet tool install -g vpk